task.summary: - Set up the Maven for work with NETConnection
- Removed thd_baseFileThread - Reorganized Controller to use Lambda function as NETConnection call.
- Completely disconnected from the inside NETConnection onto a better, from-outside version. - No longer thread based.
- Slight changes in call map. - Checkbox is now on by default.
- Checkbox send is now passed as int to sendFile function.
- Checkbox is now on by default. Different take.
